author: watson-ij
body:
#### PR description:

Move GEMDigi dictionary generating classes from EventFilter/GEMRawToDigi to DataFormats/GEMDigi and update references

Per issue #30586 only DataFormats should have objects generating dictionaries.

@jshlee @quark2
